```typescript
<FormField
  control={form.control}
  name="companyId"
  render={({ field }) => (
    <FormItem>
      <FormLabel>Şirket *</FormLabel>
      <Select onValueChange={field.onChange} value={field.value}>
        <FormControl>
          <SelectTrigger>
            <SelectValue placeholder="Şirket seçin" />
          </SelectTrigger>
        </FormControl>
        <SelectContent>
          {companies?.map((c) => (
            <SelectItem key={c.id} value={c.id}>{c.name}</SelectItem>
          ))}
        </SelectContent>
      </Select>
      <FormMessage />
    </FormItem>
  )}
/>
```

### DatePicker

shadcn Popover + Calendar + date-fns. Ayrı component (`<DateField>`) oluştur, formda kullan.

### File Upload

Özel component `<FileUpload>` — upload initiate → S3 → mark-scanning → scan poll. Documents upload flow başka rule'da.

## Banned Patterns

- Inline Zod schema — shared-schemas'tan import zorunlu
- `form.reset()` success sonrası — redirect et
- Uncontrolled inputs (`defaultValue` sadece RHF ile)
- Async validation (`rules: { validate: async }`) — submit'te server handle
- `<form action={serverAction}>` — server actions MVP'de yok
- Sadece toast, field error mapping yok — field-specific code için setError zorunlu
- Multiple forms aynı route'ta (split into routes)
- Form state Zustand'da — RHF kullan

